
'''傑森·劉易斯'''（Jason Mark Lewis，{{bd|1955年|9月23日}}）<ref>Ancestry.com. Minnesota, Marriage Index, 1958-2001 [database on-line]. Provo, UT, USA: Ancestry.com Operations Inc, 2007</ref>是[[美國|美國]][[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]的一位[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]政治家、前廣播脫口秀節目主播、作家。在2009年到2014年，他主持廣播節目傑森·劉易斯秀<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lambert|first1=Brian|title='I wanted to make a political statement': a Q&A with former radio host Jason Lewis|url=https://www.minnpost.com/media/2015/09/i-wanted-make-political-statement-qa-former-radio-host-jason-lewis|work=MinnPost|date=September 2, 2015|accessdate=2016-11-10|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216001828/https://www.minnpost.com/media/2015/09/i-wanted-make-political-statement-qa-former-radio-host-jason-lewis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年，他當選為[[明尼蘇達州第二國會選區|明尼蘇達州第二國會選區]]的美國眾議院議員<ref>Montgomery, David. "[http://www.twincities.com/2016/11/08/minnesotas-congressional-races-2nd-district-early-results/ GOP’s Jason Lewis wins MN 2nd Congressional District; incumbent Democrats narrowly hold seats] {{Wayback|url=http://www.twincities.com/2016/11/08/minnesotas-congressional-races-2nd-district-early-results/ |date=20201105010352 }}", TwinCites.com, November 8, 2016. Retrieved November 9, 2016.</ref>。
